Meanwhile Sunhawk, and Snowowl's sparks begin circling
closer and closer together as Snoowl begins the story.

Snowowl:  A group of Vok called the Sarga went back in
time to save me.  They're going to merge us and give
us a new body that exceeds our wildest dreams.  You'll
be in charge of the basic battle, while I'll act as an
onboard computer.  Their high council is currently
debating give us a weapon that can allow us to destroy
rival Vok.

OOC: Actually I'm waiting for rAuq to respond to my
latest revision of the Vok destroyer which involves a
simulated black hole caused by the attractions of
Protons and Electrons, but lets not go into details
until he give me a yes I'll take it to the council, or
no you'll have to revise it again.
